      "value": "<p>You perform a swift burst of 2 shots that leave the enemy staggering. Make two ranged Taijutsu Attacks using your weapon, dealing your [weapons damage] +1d6. If a target is hit at least once, it must also succeed a Strength saving throw reducing the targets speed by 10 feet, for each successful attack, until the end of their next turn.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the target suffers a -1 penalty on their save.</p>",
